figgy.title: CDL Automated Ingest

comments.body: Regarding open question 2, this is a good name, and the share has been created.  The figgy service account utilized in the current ocr_pdf workflow has been granted read/write access to the share.

Some answers:

* 1: I've created a [CDL collection](https://figgy.princeton.edu/catalog/fad1929d-01ca-4888-aa32-f59e51bca7c9) that items should be added to.
* 3: Let's leave OCR language blank for now. I suspect we don't need to set this unless we want to do OCR to help creating a text alternative for accessibility reasons.
* 4: Yes, it's OK to email when an item is marked complete
